00:04:49.890 --> 00:04:52.993 align:start position:25% line:-1
行配置システムを説明するには

00:04:53.093 --> 00:04:56.330 align:start position:27% line:-1
例を挙げるのが一番でしょう

00:04:56.496 --> 00:05:00.234 align:start position:23% line:-2
